" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Ovarian cyst in female fetus at 34 weeks' gestational age",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 372px; height: 302px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Coronal sonogram shows complex cystic mass (arrow) in left abdomen (s = stomach, b = bladder). Through-transmission is seen posterior to cyst. On follow-up scans (not shown), cyst size remained the same but hematoma in cyst decreased in size. Excision was performed when infant was 3 months old, and pathology revealed intrauterine ovarian torsion.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
