"      American Academy of Pediatrics, Rose SR, Section on Endocrinology and Committee on Genetics, American Thyroid Association, et al, \"Update of Newborn Screening and Therapy for Congenital Hypothyroidism,\"",
"      <i>",
"       Pediatrics",
"      </i>",
"      , 2006, 117(6):2290-303.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
"       <a href=\"UTD.htm?21/38/22118/abstract-text/16740880/pubmed\" id=\"16740880\" target=\"_blank\">",
